@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_toyesf(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.sin((tmp + 0.32 - v1 + 0.41)) - 0.61)
    v0 = 0.06
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.sin((v2 + 0.54 * v0 + 0.85)))
    tmp = ((wp.abs(v2 + 0.11) / v2) * ((v0 + 0.99 / v1 + 0.99) - (v1 + 0.77 / v1 + 0.03)))
    v2 = v0
    v2 = (wp.exp(wp.exp(v1 + 0.81)) * wp.cos(wp.exp(v1 + 0.44)))
    data[tid] = v0
